\par \pard\plain \s17\sa120 \f7\fs20\lang3081 The object of the game is to be the first player to score a certain amount of points (usually 500). Points are scored by ridding yourself of all the cards in your hand before the computer.
\par To learn how to use Help, press {\fs18 F1}.
